      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model selected based on literature consensus for rotating blood-contacting devices. Power-law hemolysis model (Giersiepen-Wurzinger) is the regulatory standard. Formal model-form uncertainty quantification deferred per MRL 2 scoping."
