    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 4 guidance for Class II devices with medium model influence. UQ results demonstrate that the 95% confidence interval on the relative hemolysis index remains below the RH < 1 acceptance criterion across all five operating points, providing adequate confidence for the CPB use decision. The package is accepted for regulatory submission.",
